:9,"url":99,"cover":100},"542058337","大和撫子はあこがれ","遥そら","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=542058337","https://p3.music.126.net/r4KRde43oriYxAgyD8-MOA==/109951163169043939.jpg?param=90y90",{"id":102,"title":103,"artist":104,"source":9,"url":105,"cover":106},"1958727599","明日への扉","高橋李依","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=1958727599","https://p3.music.126.net/fNvDL1E9IX-__sUBPhLAGw==/109951167585364773.jpg?param=90y90",{"id":108,"title":109,"artist":110,"source":9,"url":111,"cover":112},"1818615632","色香水","神山羊","https://api.obdo.cc/meting/?server=netease&type=url&id=1818615632","https://p3.music.126.net/z-GWtONkPJHkPS8G9v55qw==/109951166198068699.jpg?param=90y90",null,{"id":115,"title":116,"body":117,"categories":208,"date":210,"description":211,"draft":212,"extension":213,"hide-info":212,"image":113,"meta":214,"navigation":216,"path":217,"permalink":113,"readingTime":218,"recommend":113,"references":113,"seo":223,"sitemap":224,"stem":225,"subtitle":113,"tags":226,"type":229,"updated":113,"__hash__":230},"content/posts/2025/10/rust-waline-deploy.md","Waline-Mini 部署体验：基于 Rust 的 Waline 评论系统？",{"type":118,"value":119,"toc":202},"minimark",[120,124,136,143,146,149,152,155,158,161,172,175,181,188,193,196],[121,122,123],"h2",{"id":123},"前言",[125,126,127,128,135],"p",{},"最近逛 Github 也是看到个离谱的东西：waline-mini，上面描述是使用 Rust 实现的高性能 Waline 评论系统，作者是",[129,130,134],"a",{"href":131,"rel":132},"https://github.com/JQiue",[133],"nofollow","jQiue","。",[125,137,138,139],{},"Github 开源地址：",[129,140,141],{"href":141,"rel":142},"https://github.com/JQiue/waline-mini",[133],[125,144,145],{},"说实话给我看懵了，Waline 我是认识的，也是很早期开始发展的 Node.js 评论系统了，在早期因为我的一些个人原因我的大部分站点最终选定的是 Twikoo 作为评论系统。",[125,147,148],{},"不过 Waline 确实是一个还不错的评论系统，本身也能在各路云函数上运行，配置要求已经可以说是很低了，但是我是真没想到如今还有大佬写出了 Rust 实现的版本。",[125,150,151],{},"文档介绍其内存占用只有 Node.js 版本 Waline 内存占用的 1/25（5612kb=5.48mb 内存占用），我只能说不愧是 Rust。",[121,153,154],{"id":154},"部署",[125,156,157],{},"我们选择一种更快速，更经济的尝试来部署下 Waline-mini，今天我们使用 Zeabur 来进行尝试，看看部署后 Zeabur 给出的消耗预算是多少，本质其实还是使用 Docker 来部署。",[125,159,160],{},"项目给出的 Docker Compose 文件如下，不一定是最新的，建议查看官方文档。",[162,163,169],"pre",{"className":164,"code":166,"language":167,"meta":168},[165],"language-yaml","services:\n  waline:\n    image: jqiue/waline-mini:latest\n    container_name: waline-mini\n    ports:\n      - '8360:8360'\n    volumes:\n      - waline-db:/app/db\n    environment:\n      - DATABASE_URL=${DATABASE_URL:-sqlite:////app/db/waline.sqlite?mode=rwc}\n      - JWT_TOKEN=${JWT_TOKEN}\n      - SITE_NAME=${SITE_NAME}\n      - SITE_URL=${SITE_URL}\n    restart: unless-stopped\n\nvolumes:\n  waline-db:\n    driver: local\n","yaml","",[170,171,166],"code",{"__ignoreMap":168},[125,173,174],{},"前往 Zeabur，创建项目，选择使用“Docker 容器镜像”部署，本文主要是部署体验文，不详细撰述该如何部署，且目前项目仍是开发状态，未来部署方式也可能会有变化。",[125,176,177],{},[178,179],"img",{"alt":168,"src":180},"https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/2025/10/r-waline/zeabur-docker.webp",[125,182,183,184,187],{},"部署后我们可以通过",[170,185,186],{"code":186},"waline.example.com/ui","访问后台并注册账号，第一个注册的用户即为 Waline 管理员",[125,189,190],{},[178,191],{"alt":168,"src":192},"https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/2025/10/r-waline/waline-ui.webp",[125,194,195],{},"可以看到 Waline 还原完整度确实很高了，后台基本 100% 还原。",[125,197,198,199],{},"还有你们最关心的资源占用图，可以看到平均内存使用量为 3.48MB，确实很低了。\n",[178,200],{"alt":168,"src":201},"https://blog-files.101045700.xyz/2025/10/r-waline/zeabur-used.webp",{"title":168,"searchDepth":203,"depth":203,"links":204},4,[205,207],{"id":123,"depth":206,"text":123},2,{"id":154,"depth":206,"text":154},[209],"技术探索","2025-10-25T03:00:00","本文介绍了作者因 GitHub 上的 waline-mini 项目而产生的惊喜与实测过程。作为一款使用 Rust 重写的 Waline 评论系统，waline-mini 据称内存占用仅为 Node.js 原版的 1/25（约 5.5MB）。文章记录了作者通过 Zeabur 平台使用 Docker 快速部署的体验：配置简洁、支持 SQLite、默认监听 8360 端口，首个注册账户即成为管理员。实测后台 UI 与原版高度一致，平均内存仅 3.48 MB，验证了 Rust 带来的极致轻量，适合对资源占用敏感的站点。",false,"md",{"slots":215},{},true,"/2025/10/rust-waline-deploy",{"text":219,"minutes":220,"time":221,"words":222},"3 min read",2.345,140700,469,{"title":116,"description":211},{"loc":217},"posts/2025/10/rust-waline-deploy",[227,228],"自托管","评论系统","tech","kMHUBBKBSsJyRzJWiRVJ7JSbQTj27GPjmy-Xx-jVDp0",[232,238],{"title":233,"path":234,"stem":235,"date":236,"type":237,"children":-1},"迟来的个人对《拔作岛》第一部游戏动漫杂谈","/2025/10/nukitashi-gv-end","posts/2025/10/nukitashi-gv-end","2025-10-25T02:00:00","story",{"title":239,"path":240,"stem":241,"date":242,"type":237,"children":-1},"博客～真周年随笔（大概是一周年）","/2025/11/blog-1th-note","posts/2025/11/blog-1th-note","2025-11-04T08:00:00",1766999809999]